vote.title: Authorize a one-year service contract, with two one-year renewal options, for homeless services targeting young adults twenty-four years of age and younger for the Office of Homeless Solutions - CitySquare, most advantageous proposer of three - Not to exceed $270,554 - Financing:  FY21 Texas Department of Housing and Community Affairs TDHCA Funds
